&gt;      Dark Chao:
&gt;           Pet it with Eggman, Shadow, or Rouge. It will start getting Black, and a red line will appear around its neck. You can give it anything you want. Animals, Drives, and stuff, but with the characters described above. Here's a list of Dark Chao Types:
&gt; 
&gt; Power Type: Give it, while child, Red Drives, only.
&gt; Flying Type: Give to young Chao Purple Drives only.
&gt; Running type:Give to young Chao Green Drives only.
&gt; Swimming Type: Give to young chao Yellow Drives Only.
&gt; Normal type: Give only Chao fruits to young Chao.
&gt; 
&gt;      These only work if you give the Chaos Drives with the Evil Characters. There are more kinds of Chao. Look for my other post.

